1. *Sebi* se vrati kući. (He returned home to himself.)
2. *Sebi* je dao obećanje. (He promised himself.)
3. Zabranio je *sebi* da ide. (He forbade himself to go.)
4. Pomogao je *sebi* da dođe do cilja. (He helped himself to reach the goal.)
5. Sprečio je *sebi* da ode. (He prevented himself from leaving.)
6. *Sebi* je dao nadu. (He gave himself hope.)
7. *Sebi* je postavio cilj. (He set himself a goal.)
8. *Sebi* je govorio da je sve u redu. (He was telling himself that everything was okay.)